            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#6B7280]">6.2 Potential additional costs based on security posture</h3>
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 border border-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
