            <p class="text-[#6B7280] leading-relaxed mb-4">
              The baseline above is sufficient for an unrestricted deployment with no enterprise-grade security overlays. As clients formalise their security requirements, certain additional Azure resources or higher-tier resource selections may be needed. The table below shows the indicative monthly addition per instance for each common upgrade. Costs are additive: a deployment requiring multiple upgrades will combine them.
