              <li><strong>Defer other work to a future development contract.</strong> Any request from Cloud9 during the MVP build for work outside Section 3 is acknowledged and deferred. It is not refused. It is scheduled into a future development engagement.</li>
              <li><strong>No verbal scope expansions.</strong> All change requests are made in writing per Section 3.4. No verbal &ldquo;while you're at it&rdquo; additions.</li>
              <li><strong>Single point of acceptance.</strong> The Cloud9 PoC handover and the Cleanaway production deployment together form the acceptance events for this contract. Once those are signed off and the final milestone is paid, this contract is closed. Any further Visualisation Tool work runs under a separately agreed development contract.</li>
